This looks good, but we need to remove the changes to thirdy_party/onnx in the diff.
You want to do:

git diff origin/master third_party/onnx
cd third_party/onnx
git checkout ${onnx_commit_hash_of_master}
cd ../..
git commit -a --amend

body:
This looks good, but we need to remove the changes to thirdy_party/onnx in the diff. 
You want to do:
```
git diff origin/master third_party/onnx
cd third_party/onnx
git checkout ${onnx_commit_hash_of_master}
cd ../..
git commit -a --amend
```
